    "caption_text": "Zara unveils a new flagship store in Barcelona. \nDesigned by Belgian architect Vincent Van Duysen @vincentvanduysen, the store brings the calm beauty of private interiors to the iconic Avenida Diagonal. Its layout unfolds like a layered home, with a sequence of rooms that varies deliberately, evoking the warmth and intimacy of lived-in spaces.\n\n#zara",
