    "voiceover_text": "I believe architecture has to be super emotional. I'm Vincent van Duizen, I'm a Belgian architect-designer. Architecture is for me not only the physical structure of the space. For me architecture is contributing to the quality of life of its inhabitants. I want to guarantee an absolute sense of comfort and well-being and also a sense of protection. A very sensorial world where the spaces have to be fulfilled and filled with emotions. I created a new home for Zara which is called Zara Diagonal. It's a world of desire, it's a world to be surprised and it's a world where you want to come back multiple times. Zara Diagonal",
